1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=I Know Exactly How Much You Hurt=

4
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:53,013
(That man in black shares
the same source of power as mine.)

5
00:00:53,353 --> 00:00:55,166
(He even plotted
to separate me from Zhaoli.)

6
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:57,520
(It seems he knows my condition well.)

7
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:07,520
Ying Du.

8
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,870
So, we're back in the tribe?

9
00:01:16,430 --> 00:01:17,270
I'm sorry.

10
00:01:18,510 --> 00:01:19,790
I failed to protect you.

11
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:22,960
It's fine.

12
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,280
I'm not in pain.

13
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:27,640
I know how much you hurt

14
00:01:28,430 --> 00:01:29,680
better than anyone.

15
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,960
Ying Du.

16
00:01:43,350 --> 00:01:44,190
Hold still.

17
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,000
It'll sting a little.

18
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:01,270
Ying Du,

19
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:04,280
I'd been wondering

20
00:02:04,710 --> 00:02:06,130
why you always arrived just in time

21
00:02:06,143 --> 00:02:07,280
every time I got hurt.

22
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:09,400
Only today did I realize

23
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,360
that when I'm hurt,
you feel the pain too.

24
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,840
Is that really true?

25
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:19,960
So,

26
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:22,280
when you said you'd protect me,

27
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,430
it wasn't just because of the power.

28
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:27,750
You also didn't want
to get hurt yourself.

29
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:32,680
At first, that was true,

30
00:02:33,430 --> 00:02:34,310
but later,

31
00:02:34,497 --> 00:02:35,586
every time you faced danger,

32
00:02:35,597 --> 00:02:36,690
it was always because of me.

33
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:38,680
Today, to save me,

34
00:02:39,396 --> 00:02:40,623
you even nearly lost your life.

35
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,080
Zhaoli,

36
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:44,190
I don't want you to be hurt ever again.

37
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,440
Ying Du!

38
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:49,710
I'm here to save you!

39
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:53,750
Ying Du,

40
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,750
hang in there.

41
00:02:55,796 --> 00:02:57,176
You ran all the way here like that?

42
00:02:57,230 --> 00:02:58,803
Were you not afraid of losing your life?

43
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:04,990
Zhaoli,

44
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,470
it was too dangerous today.

45
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:09,470
From now on,
you must put yourself first.

46
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,870
I can handle everything else.

47
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:14,470
Since I made a pact with you,

48
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,680
I'm bound to help you.

49
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,590
Is this only because of the pact?

50
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:25,630
Not entirely.

51
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:28,470
Then...

52
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,200
Ying Du.

53
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:34,240
Ying Du, what's wrong with you?

54
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,800
Ying Du!

55
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,910
Do you need to use your power?

56
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,040
Don't get me wrong.

57
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,720
I only wish to heal your wounds.

58
00:05:45,170 --> 00:05:48,770
笙ｪA weary bird sways the branches笙ｪ

59
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:54,250
笙ｪMy heart feels a gentle bond笙ｪ

60
00:05:55,770 --> 00:05:58,310
笙ｪPetals fall before the courtyard笙ｪ

61
00:05:58,550 --> 00:06:00,970
笙ｪNew sprouts cover the ground笙ｪ

62
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:04,600
笙ｪI can't tell what's real or false笙ｪ

63
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:10,290
笙ｪYou lean close, speaking softly笙ｪ

64
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:16,050
笙ｪYour gaze blooms with grace笙ｪ

65
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,080
Your Majesty.

66
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,400
Who is it?

67
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:22,270
Who?

68
00:06:23,490 --> 00:06:24,360
It's me.

69
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,200
Luo Cheng.

70
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,680
I have matters to report.

71
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,240
He's here for you.

72
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:32,670
Go now.

73
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,350
Your Majesty,

74
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:47,750
I was worried. Your power had waned,

75
00:06:48,243 --> 00:06:49,716
so your grave injuries from yesterday

76
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,070
might not heal so soon.

77
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:53,310
Yet you've recovered so well.

78
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:54,490
It seems

79
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:57,120
Zhaoli must have tended to you
with care last night.

80
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,060
Get to the matter.

81
00:07:03,070 --> 00:07:05,240
I couldn't find anyone
who uses the same spells as you.

82
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,070
His power is remarkably strong.

83
00:07:08,773 --> 00:07:10,446
Now, I share a spiritual link
with Zhaoli;

84
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,240
it's hard to say if I can match him.

85
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,553
Your Majesty,

86
00:07:13,564 --> 00:07:15,673
that man lurking in the shadows
is far too dangerous.

87
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,040
(The top priority)

88
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,360
(is to find the man in black.)

89
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,240
Protect Zhaoli.

90
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,600
Don't let her step outside,

91
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:25,070
and above all, keep her from harm.

92
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,520
Yes.

93
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,360
I am Oracle,

94
00:07:31,433 --> 00:07:32,870
well-versed in the past and present.

95
00:07:32,870 --> 00:07:34,160
There's nothing I don't know.

96
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:37,240
May I ask what you seek to know?

97
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,560
Under what circumstances

98
00:07:38,866 --> 00:07:40,740
would two people's power
share the same origin?

99
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,480
I have, in fact,

100
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,430
heard of it before.

101
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:47,190
Only the closest of blood kin,

102
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:50,920
parents or siblings,

103
00:07:51,190 --> 00:07:54,000
may share the same power.

104
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:56,870
No others could ever have it.

105
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,360
(Siblings?)

106
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,040
(Why does my body suddenly burn
with restless heat?)

107
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:09,390
(Is Zhaoli...)

108
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,110
Zhaoli.

109
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:23,870
You're back?

110
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,240
You were waiting for me?

111
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:36,320
Why did you leave alone in daylight?

112
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:39,790
You even kept me inside

113
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:42,440
and left me till late at night.

114
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,910
Don't leave me like that again.

115
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:49,390
I fear harm may come to you.

116
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,080
Zhaoli,

117
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,910
say that again.

118
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,670
From now on, do not leave

119
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,840
without telling me.

120
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:09,010
笙ｪSnow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly笙ｪ

121
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:15,810
笙ｪMemories turn,
forgiving time after time笙ｪ

122
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:20,550
笙ｪTears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter笙ｪ

123
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:23,450
笙ｪHard to tell them apart笙ｪ

124
00:09:23,970 --> 00:09:29,260
笙ｪVowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness笙ｪ

125
00:09:29,260 --> 00:09:32,960
笙ｪIn this life, I still run toward you笙ｪ

126
00:09:33,310 --> 00:09:35,660
笙ｪNo matter the homeward journey笙ｪ

127
00:09:35,660 --> 00:09:39,700
笙ｪFalling to the deepest place
in your heart笙ｪ

128
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:42,080
笙ｪAnd that is enough笙ｪ

129
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:45,870
笙ｪAhead lies a path without snow or wind笙ｪ

130
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,840
笙ｪBegonia blooms across the branches笙ｪ

131
00:09:49,210 --> 00:09:54,960
笙ｪOne more glance
may let love stand still笙ｪ

